      <S N="ReleaseNotes"># 1.1.0_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_* Features and Improvements_x000D__x000A_  * Add support for Important Notifications using the Urgent switch._x000D__x000A_  * Add support for setting button colors._x000D__x000A_  * Center align notification body text when using the IncomingCall scenario._x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_# 1.0.1_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_* Bug Fixes_x000D__x000A_  * OnActivated events are "sticky"_x000D__x000A_    * See #256 by [Windos](https://github.com/Windos)_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_# 1.0.0_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_* Breaking Changes_x000D__x000A_  * Custom Audio Path Removed: Support for custom audio file sources has been eliminated._x000D__x000A_  * AppId Customization Removed: The ability to specify a custom AppId has been removed._x000D__x000A_  * Shoulder Tap Notifications Removed: Support for "shoulder tap" toast types is no longer available._x000D__x000A_* Features and Improvements_x000D__x000A_  * Create and update all help files._x000D__x000A_  * Enable "Activation" events on all supported versions of PowerShell, including Windows PowerShell._x000D__x000A_  * Enable "Dismissed" and "Failed" events on PowerShell 7.1+._x000D__x000A_  * Improve support for attribution text._x000D__x000A_  * Shortcut Support: Introduced capability to create Windows shortcuts with proper AppUserModelID—enables full toast branding when launching PowerShell._x000D__x000A_  * Event Data Improvements: Event data handling and options improved for notification actions._x000D__x000A_* CI and Repository_x000D__x000A_  * Update Issue and Feature Request Templates._x000D__x000A_* Libraries_x000D__x000A_  * Microsoft.Windows.SDK.NET.Ref library bumped to 10.0.22621.28._x000D__x000A_  * Microsoft.Toolkit.Uwp.Notifications library bumped to 7.1.3._x000D__x000A_</S>
